cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.RO

The paper discusses a novel approach for reinforcement learning using convolutional neural networks and reservoir computing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves visual feature extraction using CNNs, which suggests the possibility of cs.CV (Computer Vision) as a sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed approach in robotics, which indicates the possibility of cs.RO (Robotics).
